      <abstract>The Watson Park Church was gathered in 1912 in the Dunning neighborhood of Chicago,
        Illinois. The church dissolved around 2014 or 2015. The collection contains vital membership
        records such as baptismal records, confirmation records, a membership register, wedding
        records, and funeral remembrances.</abstract>
